txt.en: This contains two packages that contain two copies of each of the following: Fanned Shield Display, Fanned Ornate Shield Display, Shield Display with Halberds, Ornate Shield Display with Halberds, Ornate Shield Display with Swords, Shield Display with Simple Swords, Shield Display with Gold-hilt Swords, Ornate Shield Display with Simple Swords, Ornate Shield Display with Gold-hilt Swords, Shield Display with Various Swords, and Ornate Shield Display with Various Swords.
